description.text:
I saw CHSEngineering's wall mount for their Keyboard and mouse and while I just printed the keyboard mount I wanted to do something a little more custom for my mouse. 
The dimensions didn't come out exactly as I had hoped but it did come out well enough to get the job done. I'd recommend opening up the cup portion just a little more but the angle seems to be about right and it's &quot;good enough&quot; if you want something to be able to just print. 
Units should be in &quot;mm.&quot;
